data.description:
Welcome to your future oasis, nestled on a peaceful .34-acre lot,  with trees, lush greenery, and a delightful creek gently flowing behind the property. This charming one-story ranch home boasts a brand new roof and is equipped with a central vacuum system, perfect for efficient cleaning.

Step inside and revel in the warmth of this home's lovingly designed interior, complete with a large eat-in kitchen, perfect for hosting family dinners or entertaining guests. The dining room boasts spacious, open layout seating, inviting you to stretch out and relax.

As you make your way through the home, you'll discover two bedrooms in the main house, each ready to provide you peaceful respite whenever you desire. Nestled adjacent to these is a cozy captive bedroom or bonus room beckoning you with its unique charm and tranquility.

When the night falls, you can retire to the large master bedroom, where sweet dreams live. With ample space and cozy natural lighting, this master bedroom is ideal for curling up with a good book or just basking in its relaxation energy.

But wait, that's not all! Additional living space is available in the form of a gorgeous and spacious mother-in-law suite, featuring one bedroom, a fully equipped kitchen, and a grand living room that's perfect for spending time with friends and family.

The breezeway that runs between the house and the suite is simply stunning, welcoming you with a gentle breeze and calming natural beauty. The fully finished basement with its roaring fireplace offers a perfect place to curl up on a chilly evening. Here you'll also find the laundry, well equipped to handle all your needs.

The large and inviting back deck, partially covered and featuring stunning views of  the enchanting creek, is an invitation to take in the beauty that nature has to offer. A grand shed and fire pit provide additional outdoor space and opportunity for adventure.

Say goodbye to pesky maintenance and gutter clogs with innovative gutter guards in place—because relaxation comes first in your peaceful new home, surrounded by the calming sounds of the bubbling creek.
